com.orchestranetworks.workflow
Interface ProcessInstance

public interface ProcessInstance

Represents a workflow and provides some information about it.

Method Summary
 Date getCreationDate()
          Returns the creation date of the workflow.
 UserReference getCreator()
          Returns the user that created the workflow.
 DataContext getDataContext()
          Returns the DataContext of the process instance.
 UserMessage getDescription()
          Returns the description of the workflow.
 UserMessage getLabel()
          Returns the label of the workflow.
 Date getLastModificationDate()
          Returns the last modified date of the workflow.
 Integer getPriority()
          Returns the current priority of the workflow if defined, otherwise returns null.
 Integer getPriorityOrDefaultPriority()
          Returns the current priority of the workflow or the default priority if defined, else null.
 ProcessInstanceKey getProcessInstanceKey()
          Returns the identifier of the workflow.
 PublishedProcessKey getPublishProcessKey()
          Returns the identifier of the associated workflow publication.
 List getWorkItems()
          Returns the list of associated UserTask.WorkItems.
 boolean isCompleted()
          Returns true if the workflow is completed, returns false otherwise.
